      "claimText": "The CFD hemolysis model, validated against FDA generic pump benchmark data, is sufficiently credible to rank hemolysis severity across the five specified flow-speed combinations and to support the regulatory submission claim that the proposed device geometry does not exceed predicate hemolysis levels (RH < 1) under worst-case operating conditions.",
